node.text: @reginachow_sg hehe try! It’s the healthier version!

Not usually a fan of instant noodles but @theofficialkoka Delight is an exception cuz’ it’s made with whole grain and they’re non-fried (steamed & baked instead!), making it the healthier choice 👍 - and that’s why it’s a popular choice when working from home on days when I’ve too much work, too little time to cook. 😅
- 
I like my noodles to be paired with LOTS of veggies & some protein to make it a well balanced meal. 😋 Swipe ⬅️ left to check out my version of healthy noodles and the ingredients I’ve put in. 👩‍🍳
